ns un peu l\\u00e0, que je te mange !\\r\\n- \\u00c7a va pas ? Tu es maboul ?\\r\\n- Maboul ? Retire \\u00e7a !\\r\\n- Abruti ! \\u00bb\\r\\nCocorico\\r\\nCocorico\\r\\nCot\\r\\n\\u00ab Ouh l\\u00e0 l\\u00e0 !\\r\\nLe m\\u00e9dicament n\'a pas march\\u00e9 ?\\r\\nIl va y avoir du boulot pour refermer ce bazar ! \\u00bb<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                        <h2>Chapter 2: The Adventure<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>One day, while exploring the enchanted forest, our hero made an amazing discovery...<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                        <h2>Chapter 3: The Lesson<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>And so, after this wonderful adventure, everyone learned that the most important thing is to believe in yourself and never stop learning!<\\/p>\",\"age_range\":\"3-13\",\"reading_time\":3,\"thumbnail\":\"stories\\/wSrjPu0NpiiQVzoSM62NdD2xchCvMrp4N0T2RWLL.png\",\"views\":40,\"rating\":5,\"rating_count\":8,\"is_published\":true,\"created_at\":\"2025-04-26T01:08:35.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-04-26T01:09:55.000000Z\",\"audio_file\":\"stories\\/audio\\/PqtFEIUe7C7ZDDq8IAlFyiiTyiCCnAybRVK1XILz.mp3\",\"audio_duration\":null,\"audio_url\":null,\"video_file\":null,\"video_duration\":null,\"video_url\":null},{\"id\":2,\"category_id\":1,\"title\":\"Story 2 in Albums et histoires\",\"slug\":\"story-2-in-albums-et-histoires\",\"description\":\"This is a sample story in the Albums et histoires category. It\'s perfect for kids who love reading!\",\"content\":\"<h2>Chapter 1: The Beginning<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>Once upon a time, in a magical world far away, there lived a curious child who loved to learn new things...<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                        <h2>Chapter 2: The Adventure<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>One day, while exploring the enchanted forest, our hero made an amazing discovery...<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                        <h2>Chapt