\\r\\nDans les for\\u00eats, s\'enfuyaient tout tremblants.\\r\\n\\r\\nREFRAIN\\r\\n\\r\\nUn \\u00e9l\\u00e9phant parut : et sur la terre,\\r\\nSe pr\\u00e9para ce combat de g\\u00e9ants.\\r\\nMais pr\\u00e8s de l\\u00e0 courait une rivi\\u00e8re,\\r\\nLe crocodile s\'y jeta subitement.\\r\\n\\r\\nREFRAIN\\r\\n\\r\\nEt tout rempli d\'une crainte salutaire,\\r\\nS\'en retourna vers ses petits enfants.\\r\\nNotre \\u00e9l\\u00e9phant, d\'une trompe plus fi\\u00e8re,\\r\\nVoulut alors accompagner ce chant.\\r\\n\\r\\nREFRAIN\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"age_range\":\"3-13\",\"reading_time\":\"4\",\"image_url\":null,\"audio_duration\":null,\"video_duration\":null,\"image\":{\"name\":\"biblidcha_018i01.png\",\"size\":\"113.425KB\"},\"audio_file\":{\"name\":\"18.mp3\",\"size\":\"3364.992KB\"}},\"session\":{\"_token\":\"kzzyn5i6N4qS6iFZJtIjqUgqv0WpOeaWIp98fozq\",\"_previous\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1:8000\\/admin\\/stories\\/13\\/edit\"},\"_flash\":{\"old\":[\"success\"],\"new\":[]},\"login_web_59ba36addc2b2f9401580f014c7f58ea4e30989d\":1,\"success\":\"Story updated successfully.\"},\"response_headers\":{\"cache-control\":\"no-cache, private\",\"date\":\"Sat, 26 Apr 2025 02:37:58 GMT\",\"location\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1:8000\\/admin\\/stories\\/13\\/edit\",\"content-type\":\"text\\/html; charset=utf-8\",\"set-cookie\":\"XSRF-%3D; expires=Sat, 26 Apr 2025 04:37:58 GMT; Max-Age=7200; path=\\/; samesite=lax, laravell_%3D; expires=Sat, 26 Apr 2025 04:37:58 GMT; Max-Age=7200; path=\\/; httponly; samesite=lax\"},\"response_status\":302,\"response\":\"Redirected to http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1:8000\\/admin\\/stories\\/13\\/edit\",\"duration\":231,\"memory\":42,\"hostname\":\"DESKTOP-I2QG2EI\",\"user\":{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"Admin User\",\"email\":\"admin@example.com\"}}', '2025-04-26 02:37:58'),
